creator: Modelo Continente Hipermercados, SA
descriptionHtml:
With the Continente Siga application you only need your phone to build your lists and to shop in-store. With the self-scan functionality, you can do all your shopping in-store, quickly and conveniently. You also have access to promotions, coupons and product suggestions tailored to your preferences.

With Siga, you can:
- Make the purchase in-store, directly on your smartphone, by self-scanning the product’s barcode.
- Buy online with delivery at home or through the Click & Go service.
- Create and manage lists, by voice, text and barcode reading.
- Get smart search results that consider your buying preferences.
- Add multiple articles to the cart in one go, using the "mais" command, example: "leite mais manteiga".
- Find deals by adding the command "em promoções" to your search. - eg "detergente para a roupa em promoção".
- Make quick and secure payments.
- Receive personalized deal suggestions.
- View and use your available coupons.
- Use your Cartão Continente loyalty card balance to pay.
- Check current promotions.
descriptionShort: Shopping has never been so fast, easy and convenient. Meet Continente Siga.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
The balance on your loyalty card Cartao Continente can now be used for in-app payments
You can now edit and use your invoice details directly in the app
Bags can now be added to a click and pick up service order
Usability improvements in the click and pick up service
Minor interface improvements and bug fixes

title: Continente Siga

creator: Modelo Continente Hipermercados, SA
descriptionHtml:
With the Continente Siga application you only need your phone to build your lists and to shop in-store. With the self-scan functionality, you can do all your shopping in-store, quickly and conveniently. You also have access to promotions, coupons and product suggestions tailored to your preferences.

With Siga, you can:
- Make the purchase in-store, directly on your smartphone, by self-scanning the product’s barcode.
- Buy online with delivery at home or through the Click & Go service.
- Create and manage lists, by voice, text and barcode reading.
- Get smart search results that consider your buying preferences.
- Add multiple articles to the cart in one go, using the "mais" command, example: "leite mais manteiga".
- Find deals by adding the command "em promoções" to your search. - eg "detergente para a roupa em promoção".
- Make quick and secure payments.
- Receive personalized deal suggestions.
- View and use your available coupons.
- Use your Cartão Continente loyalty card balance to pay.
- Check current promotions.
